    <h1>De-Index</h1>
    <p class="description">Removing a page from Google's index so it no longer appears in search results. Can be <strong>deliberate</strong> (noindex, robots.txt) or <strong>accidental</strong> (penalty, quality drop, misconfigured tag) — and reversible in either case.</p>
